<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4488938>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 7. Male genitalia of Thysanarthria championi (Knisch, 1924).A–E – lectotype of Chaetarthria championi Knisch, 1924 (A–C – whole aedeagus in dorsal, lateral and ventral view; D – detail of median lobe and parameres in dorsal view; E – same after KOH treatment, with fully everted internal sac). F–J – lectotype of Chaetarthriomorphus sulcatus Chiesa, 1967 (F–H – whole aedeagus in dorsal, lateral and ventral view; I–J – details of parameres and median lobe in dorsal and ventral view)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4488938/files/figure.png" .

